is in probate,

56:15.411 --> 56:17.241
but why does it
have to be me?

56:17.345 --> 56:19.472
Or is it wrong
to complain?

56:19.881 --> 56:21.246
Judy says it is.

56:21.883 --> 56:23.850
But I'm so strapped
for cash right now,

56:23.918 --> 56:26.853
carrying the mortgage, and
paying for the Jolly Roger,

56:26.921 --> 56:30.357
and I wrecked the car, and
Danny's bar mitzvah coming up, I...

56:30.424 --> 56:33.256
Something like this,
there's never a good time.

56:33.927 --> 56:36.691
I don't know
where it all leaves me.

56:36.763 --> 56:37.889
Sy's death.

56:39.364 --> 56:42.390
