he stopped checking.

01:02:20.659 --> 01:02:22.149
He returned to life.

01:02:27.198 --> 01:02:29.564
These questions that are
bothering you, Larry,

01:02:30.735 --> 01:02:32.225
maybe they're
like a toothache.

01:02:33.538 --> 01:02:36.028
Feel them for a while,
then they go away.

01:02:36.540 --> 01:02:39.134
