I'm Lawrence Gopnik.

01:04:48.787 --> 01:04:50.687
Do you go by the name
Arthur Gopnik?

01:04:50.789 --> 01:04:52.256
No.

01:04:52.324 --> 01:04:53.621
Is that Arthur Gopnik?

01:04:57.662 --> 01:05:00.426
