01:08:13.265 --> 01:08:15.698
Was he helpful
at all?

01:08:18.669 --> 01:08:20.830
What, did he tell you
about the goy's teeth?

01:08:22.705 --> 01:08:24.866
You should try to
talk to Marshak.

01:08:25.140 --> 01:08:28.304
